### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 0 — HEALTH
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check — run this first, must return {"status":"ok"}
GET http://localhost:3001/health


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 1 — STOCKS  (Finnhub, 1hr cache)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### All stocks sorted by top movers
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stocks

###

### Single quote — hits Finnhub if cache is stale
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stocks/AAPL

###

### Another symbol
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stocks/TSLA

###

### Company profile — hits Finnhub if 24hr cache is stale
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stocks/AAPL/profile

###

### Weekly chart — expect 404 until chartSync.job.js runs at 2am
### To seed manually: call syncWeeklyChart(['AAPL']) from a test script
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stocks/AAPL/chart

###

### Chart with custom limit (last 12 weeks)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stocks/MSFT/chart?limit=12


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 2 — CRYPTO  (Alpha Vantage, 12hr cache)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### All crypto rates — expect 404 data until cryptoSync.job.js runs at 8am
GET http://localhost:3001/api/crypto

###

### Single crypto rate
GET http://localhost:3001/api/crypto/BTC

###

GET http://localhost:3001/api/crypto/ETH

###

GET http://localhost:3001/api/crypto/SOL


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 3 — FOREX  (Alpha Vantage, 12hr cache)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### All forex pairs — expect empty until forexSync.job.js runs at 9am
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forex

###

### GBP/USD — last 30 days of daily OHLC
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forex/GBP-USD

###

### EUR/USD
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forex/EUR-USD


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 4 — NEWS  (Finnhub, 6hr cache)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### General market news — triggers Finnhub on first call
GET http://localhost:3001/api/news

###

### Company-specific news
GET http://localhost:3001/api/news/AAPL

###

GET http://localhost:3001/api/news/TSLA

###

GET http://localhost:3001/api/news/NVDA


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 5 — IPO  (Finnhub, 24hr cache)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### IPO calendar — next 30 days
GET http://localhost:3001/api/ipo/calendar


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 6 — AUTH  (Phase 2 — uncomment when ready)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Register — run once to create your test user
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login — copy the token from the response
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get current user — paste your token below
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 7 — INSIGHTS  (Gemini AI)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Daily market summary — public, no auth needed
GET http://localhost:3001/api/insights/market

###

### Stock analysis — auth required
POST http://localhost:3001/api/insights/stock/AAPL
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

POST http://localhost:3001/api/insights/stock/TSLA
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 8 — CHAT
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Ask the AI a question
POST http://localhost:3001/api/chat
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are the top movers today?",
  "history": []
}

###

### Follow-up with history
POST http://localhost:3001/api/chat
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Tell me more about NVDA",
  "history": [
    { "role": "user",      "content": "What are the top movers today?" },
    { "role": "assistant", "content": "Today's top movers include NVDA, TSLA..." }
  ]
}


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### 9 — PORTFOLIO
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get watchlist
GET http://localhost:3001/api/portfolio/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Add to watchlist
POST http://localhost:3001/api/portfolio/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "NVDA"
}

###

### Remove from watchlist
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/portfolio/watchlist/NVDA
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get holdings
GET http://localhost:3001/api/portfolio/holdings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Add a holding
POST http://localhost:3001/api/portfolio/holdings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "shares": 10,
  "buyPrice": 175.50,
  "buyDate": "2024-01-15"
}
